          "type": "text",
          "preset": "body",
          "html": "BFS is the foundation of many graph algorithms:<br>• Shortest paths in unweighted graphs<br>• Connected component detection<br>• Level-set decomposition<br>• Network diameter estimation",
          "position": {
            "x": 80,
            "y": 200,
